  <title>pack</title>
<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(Clutter.Actor, gboolean, gboolean, gboolean, Clutter.BoxAlignment, Clutter.BoxAlignment)
@returns(none)
def pack(actor, expand, x_fill, y_fill, x_align, y_align)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Packs @actor inside the <link xref="Clutter.Container">Clutter.Container</link> associated to @layout
and sets the layout properties</p>

<table>
<tr>
<td><p>actor :</p></td>
<td><p>a <link xref="Clutter.Actor">Clutter.Actor</link></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
